<item>
            <title>[SPR-622] spring:* tags are not usable outside a dispatcher servlet request</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-622</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It&apos;d be great if spring:bind, spring:message, spring:nestedPath, etc. tags could be used outside of a dispatcher servlet request environment.  Currently they depend on a dispatcher servlet web application context.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="10982">SPR-622</key>
            <summary>spring:* tags are not usable outside a dispatcher servlet request</summary>
